metadata.name: Blended collage 01
metadata.description:
Blended collages is an ongoing project focused on the deconstruction/reconstruction of selected collages and cutouts with a nn prompted and imagetoimage AI process, post produced trough different softwares and applications such as Photoshop, After effect and others. 
Work conceived and minted for The Fun Show, curated by Haus of collage
3000x4500px
may 2023
